<div class="image-container aligncenter"><a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/ellie3-gimmick-free/emma-tannen.jpg"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/ellie3-gimmick-free/emma-tannen.jpg/medium.jpg" alt="emma-tannen.jpg" class="image" /></a></div>
